---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title='Contact'>
    <main class='container mx-auto px-4 py-8'>
        <section class='bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-6'>
            <h2 class='text-2xl font-bold text-green-600 text-center mb-6'>Contáctanos</h2>
            <p class='text-center mb-6'>
                ¿Tienes preguntas o comentarios? Nos encantaría saber de ti. Completa el siguiente formulario y nos
                pondremos en contacto contigo lo antes posible.
            </p>
            <form action='/send-message' method='POST' class='max-w-md mx-auto bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md'>
                <div class='mb-4'>
                    <label for='name' class='block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700'>Nombre</label>
                    <input
                        type='text'
                        id='name'
                        name='name'
                        placeholder='Tu nombre completo'
                        required
                        class='mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-gray-300 shadow-sm focus:border-green-500 focus:ring-green-500'
                    />
                </div>
                <div class='mb-4'>
                    <label for='email' class='block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700'>Correo Electrónico</label>
                    <input
                        type='email'
                        id='email'
                        name='email'
                        placeholder='tucorreo@ejemplo.com'
                        required
                        class='mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-gray-300 shadow-sm focus:border-green-500 focus:ring-green-500'
                    />
                </div>
                <div class='mb-4'>
                    <label for='message' class='block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700'>Mensaje</label>
                    <textarea
                        id='message'
                        name='message'
                        rows='4'
                        placeholder='Escribe tu mensaje aquí...'
                        required
                        class='mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-gray-300 shadow-sm focus:border-green-500 focus:ring-green-500'
                    ></textarea>
                </div>
                <div class='text-center'>
                    <button
                        type='submit'
                        class='w-full sm:w-auto inline-flex justify-center py-2 px-4 border border-transparent shadow-sm text-sm font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-green-500'
                    >
                        Enviar Mensaje
                    </button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>
